Sentencas: In order to improve the performance of SUS 430 alloy as a metallic interconnect material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC), a low-cost and Cr-free spinel coating of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 on SUS430 alloy substrate by sol-gel method is studied.
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 coated SUS430 alloy is evaluated in the simulated reducing (anode) and oxidizing (cathode) SOFC working environments at 750 degrees C for 1000 h about the microstructure, oxidation resistance and electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The result confirms that the spinel coating shows electrical conductivity of 105.5 S cm(-1) at 750 degrees C in air and an average CET value of 12.27 x 10(-6) K-1 at temperature range of 20-1000 degrees C. The coating layer is identified as MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 in cathode, and MnO, Cu and Co in anode atmosphere.
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: And the thickness of the oxidized scale is around 7-8 mu m after 1000 h of oxidation in both situations.
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The dense coating layer is effective in blocking the Cr migration/transport and depressing the growth of Cr2O3 and formation of MnCr2O4.
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In cathode atmosphere, the oxidation kinetics obeys the parabolic law with a rate constant as low as 1.77 x 10(-15) g(2) cm(-4)
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: s(-1) and the ASR contributed by the oxide scale is 0.3 m Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In anode atmosphere, the Delta m/A of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 coated SUS430 alloy is 0.2 mg cm(-2) for 1000 h. Generally, the overall performance of the MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 coated SUS430 alloy is superior to those of bare SUS430 and other ferritic candidate alloys.
Titulo: Oxidation of MnCu0.5Co1.5O4 spinel coated SUS430 alloy interconnect in anode and cathode atmospheres for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell
